    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated project or for parts. The engine has significant issues, including a knocking sound and a failing alternator, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. The body shows heavy wear with several large dents and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. It will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
